ver specialized classical and flamenco guitar instruction to geographically dispersed students through remote one-on-one sessions.', '$2.5B-$4.2B', 'high', 'medium', 'Adults and students (ages 15-65) seeking specialized classical or flamenco guitar instruction with intermediate to advanced skill levels', 5, '["Subscription-based recurring lesson packages with tiered pricing", "Pay-per-lesson model with discounted bulk purchase options", "Group masterclass sessions supplemented by private instruction"]', NULL, '["High competition from established music education platforms (TakeLessons, Preply, local instructors) and YouTube alternatives", "Difficulty demonstrating technical proficiency and differentiation in a crowded market", "Student acquisition costs may be high relative to lesson pricing; retention challenges due to skill progression plateaus"]', '["Conduct market research to identify instructor qualifications, certifications, and student testimonials that would differentiate this offering", "Analyze competitor pricing, student reviews, and market positioning on existing platforms (Preply, TakeLessons, Care.com)", "Validate demand through targeted surveys and landing page testing with classical/flamenco guitar communities and forums"]', NULL, 'Prospective classical and flamenco guitar students face limited access to qualified instructors, particularly outside major metropolitan areas. Geographic constraints, scheduling inflexibility, and the specialized nature of these disciplines create barriers to consistent, high-quality instruction.', NULL, 37.7712, -122.4413, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
